name: Myriad Resources UK
tag_list: tecnology, portals, web-search, uk, web-design, seo
overview:
Myriad Resources are a young technology company offering a number of different resources including jobsites, property portals and a discount voucher site.

The company is based in the UK near to Bedfordshire and has no more then five employees. They are dedicated to providing suitable solutions to help web users find suitable results to their search within any search engine.

Since their inception they have grown slowly and look to offer a number of new solutions in the future which will include website design and development for up and coming companies looking to venture on to the world wide web.
